high_descs: Turn around and go to the table on your right.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Rinse the tomato in the sink.
Go back to the table behind you.
Put the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the dining table.
Pick up the tomato on the dining table.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and wash the tomato.
Take the tomato out of the sink and go to the dining table.
Put the tomato on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the tomato on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around and go toward the fridge, then turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the tomato on the table, in front of the coffee maker.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left, then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right, go toward the wall, then turn right at the table, near the coffee maker.
Place the tomato on the table, to the right of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Clean the tomato on the table.
